channel.title: Help with setting up a no-ip
channel.description:
Ok, so I get my server running, I set up a no-ip account, created the no-ip thing, downloaded the "No-Ip DUC..." thing, checked the box, but still no one can connect to my server through the-scape.no-ip.info (but people can connect through hamachi)
Heres a picture of the no-ip set up:
[URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img92.imageshack.us/img92/7016/helpwt5.png[/img][/URL]
If you need other pictures/info let me know.
edit: Yes, I have read tutorials (like 4 about this)
